  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or NANTES - Charts 19-1, 19-2, 19-3 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.\u00a0<br>When approaching Nantes, what is a valid Special VFR minimum?</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<div> VFR traffic must maintain a minimum distance of 800 metres from clouds.</div>",
    "b": "<p>Arrivals from the east have to maintain an altitude of not more than 1000 ft AGL.</p>",
    "c": "<p>Departures to the west have to maintain an altitude of not more than 1000 ft AMSL.</p>",
    "d": "<div>The minimum ceiling for Special VFR procedures is 700 ft AMSL.</div>"
  },
  "correctOption": "c",
